 century it again became extremely fashionable, partly because it was the name of  Elizabeth Bowes-Lyon  (  1900–2002 ), who in  1936  became Queen Elizabeth as the wife of King George VI, and after his death in  1952  achieved great public affection as Queen Mother for nearly half a century. Even more influentially, it is the name of her daughter  Queen Elizabeth II  (  b. 1926 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elsie Bouve was born in 1192, in Milan, Lombardy, Italy. She had at least 2 sons with Lanzo Borri. She died on 1 January 1272, at the age of 80."},"et":{"1192–1 de janeiro de 1272":"1192–1. jaanuar 1272","1190–1261":"1190–1261","1210–1280":"1210–1280","1213–Male":"1213–Surnud","1192–1272":"1192–1272","1190":"1190","24 de julho de 1261":"24. juuli 1261","1213":"1213","1210":"1210","1272":"1272","1261":"1261","1 de janeiro de 1272":"1. jaanuar 1272","1192":"1192","1280":"1280","Invorio, Inferture Novara, Piedmont, Italy":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Itaalia","Milano, Lombardia, Itália":"Milano, Lombardia, Itaalia"},"fi":{"1192–1 de janeiro de 1272":"1192–1. tammikuuta 1272","1190–1261":"1190–1261","1210–1280":"1210–1280","1213–Male":"1213–Kuollut","1192–1272":"1192–1272","1190":"1190","24 de julho de 1261":"24. heinäkuuta 1261","1213":"1213","1210":"1210","1272":"1272","1261":"1261","1 de janeiro de 1272":"1. tammikuuta 1272","1192":"1192","1280":"1280","Invorio, Inferture Novara, Piedmont, Italy":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Italia","Milano, Lombardia, Itália":"Milano, Lombardia, Italia"},"fr":{"1192–1 de janeiro de 1272":"1192–1 janvier 1272","1190–1261":"1190–1261","1210–1280":"1210–1280","1213–Male":"1213–Décédé","1192–1272":"1192–1272","1190":"1190","24 de julho de 1261":"24 juillet 1261","1213":"1213","1210":"1210","1272":"1272","1261":"1261","1 de janeiro de 1272":"1 janvier 1272","1192":"1192","1280":"1280","Invorio, Inferture Novara, Piedmont, Italy":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Italie","Milano, Lombardia, Itália":"Milano, Lombardia, Italie","lifeSummary":"Elsie B